examples.en: Scoring the paper first makes it easier to fold.
Even the best defense can't keep that tiger from scoring.
Mills turned the game by scoring twice.
She won the match by scoring more than 30 aces.
The coach turned the team into a scoring machine.
Scoring three goals in quick succession, he made it 10-8.
Thomson's knack of scoring vital goals makes him important to the team.
We ended up skunking them, as our goalie was able to prevent the other team from scoring a single goal.
